    {
      "index": 10,
      "textBlockCount": 20,
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[0]",
          "text": "Tool Runtime：MCP / API / Browser 的统一工具网关"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[1]",
          "text": "工具调用是主动式 Agent 最大的价值来源，也是最大的风险来源。"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[2]",
          "text": "MCP Servers"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[3]",
          "text": "第三方/内部工具、数据库、项目管理、监控、CRM"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[4]",
          "text": "API Gateway"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[5]",
          "text": "OAuth、Token、速率限制、审计、Scope pinning"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[6]",
          "text": "Browser Runtime"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[7]",
          "text": "网页观察、表单操作、点击/填充/截屏"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[8]",
          "text": "File / Code Runtime"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[9]",
          "text": "文件系统、代码库、测试、Patch、PR"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[10]",
          "text": "Tool Policy Gateway"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[11]",
          "text": "工具注册表 · 允许/拒绝规则 · 权限级别 · 输入/输出 Guardrails · 审批触发 · 沙箱 · 审计日志"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[12]",
          "text": "Before Tool Use"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[13]",
          "text": "权限检查、PII 检测、Prompt Injection 检测、风险评分"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[14]",
          "text": "During Execution"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[10].text[15]",
          "text": "超时、重试、幂等键、事务、速率限制、用户接管"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Tool Runtime：MCP / API / Browser 的统一工具网关"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "textBlockCount": 31,
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[0]",
          "text": "Autonomy & Permission Ladder：逐级开放主动性"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[1]",
          "text": "从观察、建议、起草到审批执行和条件自动执行，每一层都有明确 UI 与技术边界。"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[2]",
          "text": "默认策略：MVP 只开放 L0–L3；L4 仅限低风险、可回滚、用户显式配置的重复流程。"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[3]",
          "text": "0"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[4]",
          "text": "L0 观察"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[5]",
          "text": "只读取允许上下文，不主动提示"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[6]",
          "text": "状态提示 / 数据源权限"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[7]",
          "text": "读范围、脱敏、最小上下文"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[8]",
          "text": "1"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[9]",
          "text": "L1 建议"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[10]",
          "text": "发现机会，提供解释与行动选项"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[11]",
          "text": "Suggestion Card / Agent Inbox"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[12]",
          "text": "不写入系统；只生成建议"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[13]",
          "text": "2"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[14]",
          "text": "L2 起草"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[11].text[15]",
          "text": "自动生成草稿，不执行外部写操作"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Autonomy & Permission Ladder：逐级开放主动性"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "textBlockCount": 27,
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[0]",
          "text": "Agentic UI Protocol：后端意图到前端组件的桥"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[1]",
          "text": "不要让前端解析自然语言；让 Agent Runtime 输出结构化 UI 事件。"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[2]",
          "text": "Agent Runtime"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[3]",
          "text": "规划、工具调用、结果、异常"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[4]",
          "text": "UI Protocol Stream"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[5]",
          "text": "typed events + schema + policy metadata"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[6]",
          "text": "UI Renderer"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[7]",
          "text": "卡片、计划、审批、时间线"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[8]",
          "text": "示例事件：SuggestionCreated"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[9]",
          "text": "{"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[10]",
          "text": "\"type\": \"suggestion.created\","
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[11]",
          "text": "\"priority\": \"high\","
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[12]",
          "text": "\"reason\": \"3 个企业客户反馈集中指向 onboarding\","
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[13]",
          "text": "\"evidence\": [\"crm:case/103\", \"feedback:thread/81\"],"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[14]",
          "text": "\"actions\": [\"view_evidence\", \"draft_plan\", \"ignore\"],"
        },
        {
          "path": "slides[12].text[15]",
          "text": "\"required_permission\": \"L2_DRAFT_ONLY\""
        }
      ],
      "title": "Agentic UI Protocol：后端意图到前端组件的桥"
    }
